CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper April 10, 1954, pg. 23, reads: "Command Performance - Raymond Williams leads the 'Cuban Flames' who appeared on the Command Performance show produced by the Centre Avenue YMCA at Schenley High School last week. This was one of the outstanding acts to appear on the program. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Raymond Williams and "Cuban Flames" wearing Caribbean-style costumes and playing conga drums during "Command Performance" show in Schenley High School auditorium
